    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in such incredible shape it basically looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it still drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without that hefty dealership price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
