    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is beyond reproach: the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with Turner plates. It retains its factory-spec Variable M Differential Lock and remains free of any rod bearing issues. The suspension geometry is factory-perfect, providing that signature telepathic turn-in. This is a time-capsule chassis with zero oxidation and a pristine undercarriage. A true turn-key masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
